Title: mk_oracle: use "${GREP}" instead of "grep"
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1701070131
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p16

When executed on solaris, <code>"grep"</code> does not know <code>-x</code> or <code>-F</code>. "${GREP}" points
to a version of grep that understands those options.
